extends layout

block content
  h1 Select a file to upload

  p Select a JPEG, PNG or MP4 to upload to see how we can use event-driven serverless solutions to solve real problems. 

  form(method='POST' action='upload-sample-file' enctype="multipart/form-data")
      label File:
      input#samplefile.form-control(type='file', name='samplefile' required='true' accept='.jpg,.png,.mp4')
      button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit

  if errors 
    ul
      for error in errors
        li!= error.msg